#

Lemon Herb Pork Parmesan with Rich Meat Sauce

$25.99
620 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

DairyPork

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

GourmetSavoryComfort Food

Description

A succulent pork dish featuring a zesty lemon herb crust, smothered in a rich, savory meat sauce, perfect for a gourmet meal.

Ingredients

  • Pork loin chops: 4 pieces
  • Lemon zest: 1 tablespoon
  • Fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Fresh thyme: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Parmesan cheese: 1 cup, grated
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Ground beef: 1 pound
  • Crushed tomatoes: 2 cups
  • Onion: 1, chopped
  • Red wine: 1/2 cup
  • Salt and pepper: to taste
  • Italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
